node.text:
It was just the kind of day I needed, simple and full of love! Thank you for all the Birthday wishes everyone.

The day started off with breakfast cooked for me and my 1 year old son had a blast feeding Mommy for a change! Later my 3 year old sang me happy birthday and blew out the candles on my cupcake for me 💝. 

Thank you to my squeeze @johnnyboymma for always going above and beyond. My friends and family kick ass love you all!

#birthdaygirl #birthdaywish #birthday #aug18 #leo #cupcakes #sprinklescupcakes #lessismore #blessed #family #girlmom #boymom #momlife #momlifeisthebestlife #thankful
